# Development Status: PARTIALLY IMPLEMENTED

## Overview
This directory contains utility scripts and tools for managing container-based
development environments and services in the swarm infrastructure.

## Implemented Components

- Basic utility scripts for container management
- Helper functions used by the sidecar container system

## Related Components

- Integration with `../sidecar-containers/` system
- Support for Docker Compose orchestration

## Development Debt

- Comprehensive test suite for all utilities
- Expanded utilities for environment diagnostics
- Documentation for API and integration points
- Performance monitoring utilities
- Resource optimization tooling
